Hi, I find a lot of `[Errno 32] Broken pipe` errors when i use the conn, getting from a connection_pool, to scan data in a table.
I discover that because scan operate would returns a generator, using connection_pool with it in a context manager would not happen a network access until i use the generator to fetch data. Exit the context manager, the conn will push back to pool. When i use the generator happen an error（such as TTransportException), this conn will not work, but it still in conn. Next time get this conn from pool will throw  `[Errno 32] Broken pipe` 

My demo code:
```python
conn_pool = None

def get_connetion_pool(timeout=2):
    global conn_pool
    if conn_pool is None:
        conn_pool = happybase.ConnectionPool(1)
    return conn_pool

def recent_events_v1(start, end, table, filter_str=None, limit=2000):
    with get_connetion_pool().connection() as conn:
            t = conn.table(table)
        start_row = 'ARTICLE' + str(start * 1000000)
        end_row = 'ARTICLE' + str(end * 1000000)
        return t.scan(row_start=start_row, row_stop=end_row, filter=filter_str, limit=limit)

def main():
    for i in range(5):
        try:
            filter_str = "SingleColumnValueFilter('basic', 'ArticleTypeID', =, 'binary:{value}')".format(value=struct.pack('>q', 52909257)) 
            # `52909257` this num in filter will result a  TTransportException error because its bytes contain a single quote.
            results = recent_events_v1(start=0, end=1505646570, table="test_article_java_2", filter_str=filter_str
            len([i for i in results]) 
        except:
            print traceback.format_exc()

```

```javascript
//http://web.archive.org/web/20080801073104/http://www.jdempster.com/category/code/jquery/tablesortercookiewidget/
$.tablesorter.addWidget({
  id: 'cookie',
  format: function(table) {
    var sortList = table.config.sortList;
    var tablesorterCookieJar = $.cookieJar('tablesorter');
    if ( sortList.length > 0) {
      tablesorterCookieJar.set($(table).attr('id'), sortList);
    } else {
      var sortList = tablesorterCookieJar.get($(table).attr('id'));
      if (sortList && sortList.length > 0) {
        jQuery(table).trigger('sorton', [sortList]);
      }
    }
  }
});

$(document).ready(function(){

  // workaround: the tablesorter cookie widget does not support a defaulted sortList set within the $.tablesorter() instantiation
  var tablesorterCookieJar = $.cookieJar('tablesorter');
  var sortList = tablesorterCookieJar.get('showListTable');
  if (!sortList || !sortList.length)
  sortList = [[5,1],[1,0]];

  $("#showListTable").tablesorter({
    sortList: sortList
  });

});
```

